p.d: Accompanied by Julie, Julien returns to Chaville on the eve of Jacques' grand departure. A final opportunity for Julien to make things up with his son who's racked by nerves. But the unplanned and imminent arrival of Julie's baby changes everything! Directed by: Stephen Cafiero (season 3, France, 2019) Screenplay: Frédéric Rosset, Camille Rosset Cast: Sébastien Chassagne (Julien), Marie Kauffmann (Marie), Théo Fernandez (Jacques), Nathalie Cerda (Sylvie), Matilda Marty (Emma), Allison Chassagne (Julie), Charlie Nelson (Louis), Amel Charif (Sam), Julie Farenc-Deramond (Léa), Martin Judas (Dylan), Bruni Makaya (Yanis) Genre: comedy drama
